The paper focuses on object localization and recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves attention mechanisms and information fusion, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments involve image datasets, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
